      <Version>3</Version>
      <Date>7/7/2015</Date>
      <Description>Updated the default value for the AUDIO_CUE_WELCOME_ENABLE CAL from False to True based on feedback from Cody Hansen </Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>4</Version>
      <Date>11/10/2015</Date>
      <Description>Based on feedback from Cody Hansen updated the description for this CAL to clarify the intended function of this CAL. The GIS-500 Spec. will also be updated to reflect the updated description here in the CAL Database. for this CAL.</Description>
